      "description": "CFD-predicted RH values for all five flow-speed combinations remain below 1.0, satisfying the acceptance criterion. Maximum RH observed was 0.87 at 5 LPM / 3600 RPM. Experimental bench data used for cross-validation were obtained from the FDA generic pump test corpus."
    },
