      "description": "Three mesh refinement levels (coarse 2.1 M, medium 5.8 M, fine 14.2 M cells) were evaluated. Grid convergence index (GCI) for the primary QoI was 1.4% on the fine mesh, confirming discretization error is within acceptable bounds for MRL 2."
    }
