    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4 for MRL 2 Class II devices. CFD predictions of the relative hemolysis index satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five operating conditions, with experimental agreement within ±15%. The assessment team concludes that the model has sufficient credibility for the stated context of use.",
